  <brief_title>Short Term Observational Study in DEB Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Short-term Study to Evaluate Methodologies for the Assessment of Disease Extent, Impact, and Wound Evolution in Patients With Dystrophic Epidermolysis Bullosa (DEB)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
