  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to better understand disease extent and to identify appropriate
      methodologies to evaluate (dystrophic epidermolysis bullosa) DEB in a quantitative and
      qualitative manner.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
